opam-version: "2.0"
name: "opam-solver"
version: "2.0.0~beta3"
synopsis: "opam 2.0 development libraries"
description: """
Solver and Cudf interaction. This library is based on the Cudf and Dose
libraries, and handles calls to the external solver from opam."""
